---
// Section 2: Vision & Scope
---

<div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
  <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Section 2: Vision and Scope</h2>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Product Overview</h3>
  <p class="mb-6 text-white/70">
    A complete game server hosting platform consisting of three integrated components:
  </p>

  <div class="mb-6 space-y-2">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
      <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span>
      <p class="text-white/70">
        <strong>Control Plane:</strong> Microservices-based backend managing provisioning, orchestration,
        billing, and user management
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
      <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
      <p class="text-white/70">
        <strong>Distributed Agents:</strong> Cross-platform workers (Linux + Windows) that provision and
        manage game servers
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
      <span class="mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></span>
      <p class="text-white/70">
        <strong>Unified Web Application:</strong> Blazor WASM frontend providing real-time console, server
        management, and administrative controls
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Target Users</h3>
  <div class="mb-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-4">
    <p class="mb-2 font-semibold">Primary Audiences:</p>
    <div class="grid gap-2 md:grid-cols-2">
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">- Gaming communities and clans</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">- Content creators and streamers</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">- Small-medium businesses</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">- Modding communities</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">- Indie game developers</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">- Individuals</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">- LAN event organizers</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">- Esports teams</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Core Differentiators</h3>
  <table class="mb-6 w-full border-collapse text-sm">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90"
          >Feature</th
        >
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90"
          >Advantage</th
        >
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          ><strong>.NET 8 + SignalR</strong></td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          >Real-time console, high performance, modern stack</td
        ></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          ><strong>Cross-Platform Agents</strong></td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          >Linux + Windows support (most competitors Linux-only)</td
        ></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          ><strong>Multi-Engine Support</strong></td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          >Minecraft, Valheim, ARK, Rust, Palworld, and more</td
        ></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          ><strong>Hybrid Cloud Ready</strong></td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          >Deploy agents anywhere (colo, cloud, on-prem)</td
        ></tr
      >
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Performance Targets</h3>
  <table class="mb-6 w-full border-collapse text-sm">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90">Metric</th
        >
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90">Target</th
        >
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          ><strong>Provisioning Time</strong></td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          >Server created + installing within 60 seconds (not playable yet)</td
        ></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"><strong>Uptime SLA</strong></td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top"
          >99% (MVP), 99.5% (growth target)</td
        ></tr
      >
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Non-Goals</h3>
  <div class="mb-6 space-y-1">
    <p class="text-white/70">- Web hosting (focus on game servers only)</p>
    <p class="text-white/70">- Competing on price (premium positioning)</p>
    <p class="text-white/70">- White-label / reseller program (at least initially)</p>
  </div>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Deferred Goals</h3>
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-500/35 bg-indigo-500/[0.12] p-4">
    <strong>Important:</strong> Architecture must support these future features
    <div class="mt-2 space-y-1">
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">- <strong>Mobile apps</strong> (iOS/Android)</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
        - <strong>KiP - Knowledge is Power Edition</strong> (detailed analytics/insights product)
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
